ivardefs.name: fullUrl
ivardefs.desc: The Absolute URL for the resource.  The fullUrl SHALL NOT disagree with the id in the resource - i.e. if the fullUrl is not a urn:uuid, the URL shall be version-independent URL consistent with the Resource.id. The fullUrl is a version independent referenc

ivardefs.name: request
ivardefs.desc: Additional information about how this entry should be processed as part of a transaction or batch.  For history, it shows how the entry was processed to create the version contained in the entry.

ivardefs.name: resource
ivardefs.desc: The Resource for the entry. The purpose/meaning of the resource is determined by the Bundle.type.

ivardefs.name: response
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the results of processing the corresponding 'request' entry in the batch or transaction being responded to or what the results of an operation where when returning history.

ivardefs.name: search
ivardefs.desc: Information about the search process that lead to the creation of this entry.

properties.desc: An entry in a bundle resource - will either contain a resource or information about a resource (transactions and history only).
